  "remarks": "Passport no.:Pakistani passport number CV9157521, issued on 8 Sep. 2008, expires on 7 Sep.2013 National identification no.: Pakistani national identity card number 44103-5251752-5. Has provided facilitation and financial services to Al-Qaida (QDe.004). Associated with Harakatul Jihad Islami (QDe.130.), Jaish-I-Mohammed (QDe.019), and Al-Akhtar Trust International (QDe.121). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed on: 14 Mar. 2012 (amended on 1 May 2019)",
